data.description: Beautiful home across the street from Willoughby Bay & 1 block to the Chesapeake Bay.  Open floor plan with a well appointed kitchen with granite counter tops, upgraded cabinets with soft close drawers doors & dovetailed drawers with a large island & walk-in pantry - open to the family room with a gas fireplace & deck off of the front of the home.  A large dining room & powder room rounds out the 1st floor with luxury vinyl plank for durability.  The master with en-suite (tiled shower with a custom glass door).  2 walk in closets & a balcony, along with 2 additional bedrooms, a half guest bathroom & laundry room are on the 2nd floor & the 3rd floor is the 4th bedroom.  Huge storage room on the first floor adjacent to the 2 car attached garage.
